example.code:
PS C:\> $attribute = New-Object Amazon.ElasticLoadBalancing.Model.PolicyAttribute -Property @{
         AttributeName="ProxyProtocol"
         AttributeValue="True"
    }
PS C:\> New-ELBLoadBalancerPolicy -LoadBalancerName my-load-balancer -PolicyName my-ProxyProtocol-policy -PolicyTypeName ProxyProtocolPolicyType -PolicyAttribute $attribute

PS C:\> Get-ELBResourceTag -LoadBalancerName @("my-load-balancer","my-internal-load-balancer")

LoadBalancerName             Tags
----------------             ----
my-load-balancer             {project, department}
my-internal-load-balancer    {project, department}

